import React from 'react' function CityInfo(props){ const store = props.store; return (

    {store.name}

  • temp: {props.store.temp}
  • temp min: {props.store.tempMin}
  • temp max: {props.store.tempMax}
  • pressure: {props.store.pressure}
  • humidity: {props.store.humidity}
  • sunrise: {props.store.sunrise}
  • sunset: {props.store.sunset}
  • description: {props.store.description}
  • wind speed: {props.store.windSpeed}
); } export default CityInfo;
